what to run:

pkg install git wget curl nano vim htop unzip zip tar clang make python -y
pkg install cmake openssl openssh proot termux-api -y
pkg install cmake libuv openssl -y
termux-setup-storage    [and give device storage access]
git clone https://github.com/xmrig/xmrig.git
cd xmrig
mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -DWITH_HWLOC=OFF
make -j10
nano startmining.sh  [put the script provided up]
cd ~/xmrig
chmod +x startmining.sh
cd ~/xmrig/build
./startmining.sh.   [starts the mining session]



press ctrl + c to stop mining

then run this to start another mining session(the above code was to start mining for the first time ever and to setup all required things]:

cd ~/xmrig/build
./startmining.sh
